clustering

folder <- "/Users/mac/Documents/GitHub/GIL/CCKF/dietcoke/data/chunked_freq/20211110-111217/gam_models"
models <- lapply(list.files(folder, full=TRUE), readRDS)
gam_df <- data.frame(
  formula=lapply(models, function(x){
    formula <- as.character(x$formula)
    formula <- paste(formula[[2]], formula[[1]], formula[[3]])
    return(formula)
  }) %>% unlist(),
  AIC=lapply(models, AIC) %>% unlist(),
  BIC=lapply(models, BIC) %>% unlist()
) %>%
  mutate(model_id=row_number()) %>%
  arrange(AIC, formula) %>%
  select(model_id, AIC, BIC, formula); gam_df

## 6 raw_freq ~ char + s(k, by = char, id = 1, m = 1) + s(mid_year, by = char, id = 1, m = 1)
## 7                                         raw_freq ~ char + s(k, by = char, id = 1, m = 1)
## 8                                                  raw_freq ~ s(k, char, bs = "fs", m = 1)
coef_mats <- lapply(models, function(x){
  coefs <- coef(x)
  coefs <- coefs[2:length(coefs)]
  coef_mat <- matrix(coefs, nrow=length(chars))
  return(coef_mat)
})
## Warning in matrix(coefs, nrow = length(chars)): data length [431] is not a sub-
## multiple or multiple of the number of rows [48]
## Warning in matrix(coefs, nrow = length(chars)): data length [488] is not a sub-
## multiple or multiple of the number of rows [48]
## Warning in matrix(coefs, nrow = length(chars)): data length [512] is not a sub-
## multiple or multiple of the number of rows [48]
## Warning in matrix(coefs, nrow = length(chars)): data length [498] is not a sub-
## multiple or multiple of the number of rows [48]
## Warning in matrix(coefs, nrow = length(chars)): data length [431] is not a sub-
## multiple or multiple of the number of rows [48]
## Warning in matrix(coefs, nrow = length(chars)): data length [815] is not a sub-
## multiple or multiple of the number of rows [48]
coef_dfs <- lapply(coef_mats, function(x){
  coef_df <- data.frame(x)
  rownames(coef_df) <- chars
  return(coef_df)
})

coef_mat <- coef_mats[[6]]
coef_df <- coef_dfs[[6]]
